{"name":"Arcane Background (Shaman)","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<p><b>Arcane Skill: </b>Faith (Spirit)</p><p><b>Starting Powers: </b>3</p><p><b>Power Points: </b>10</p><p>As long as there have been human beings, there have been those who are more in tune with the spirits of the plants and beasts, the seasons, the heavens, and the cycles of human physiology. These are the shamans, witch doctors, medicine men, and vodoun priests—those attuned to the barrier between the worlds, and to the world of light that lies beyond it.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"8W5oJ9AqKmpxFm29"}
