{"name":"Occultist","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<p>In their quest to check the plots of the Regin, the Sons of Liberty often recruit those who know the ways of black magic and spirits. Those with this Edge have studied dark arts and strange entities for many years, learning their ways and how to defeat them.</p><p>Occultists get a free reroll on Occult rolls.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Occult d8+"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"kxa97bYECliVVFD6"}
