{"name":"Arcane Background (Gifted Half-Born)","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<p><b>Arcane Skill: </b>Focus (Spirit)</p><p><b>Starting Powers: </b>1</p><p><b>Power Points: </b>15</p><p>Humans and Astlatians rarely mate, but when they do, their offspring occasionally exhibit incredible abilities. Not all half-elves are gifted, but all gifted are half-elves.</p><p>All gifted are creatures of both the cities and the woods, and their powers reflect it.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, The Half-Born"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"jlC61VTo5YLLmTNW"}
