{"name":"Arcane Background (Healer)","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<p><b>Arcane Skill: </b>Faith (Spirit)</p><p><b>Starting Powers: </b>3</p><p><b>Power Points: </b>10</p><p>Every world has its healers, those with soft hearts and a desire to aid those in pain. Astla is no different. The magic for healing is considered a gift by all races and healers are revered and considered off-limits in times of war.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"6mW9ZWJIX5DDhfX7"}
