{"name":"Arcane Background (PsiLock/PsiWitch)","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<p><b>Arcane Skill: </b>Psionics (Smarts)</p><p><b>Starting Powers: </b>3</p><p><b>Power Points: </b>10</p><p>Psilocks and psiwitches are those who have developed extraordinary mental skills and possess evolved minds able to perform seemingly magical feats with little more than a thought. They are rare and often feared by others.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":[],"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Ma4jO1yx4tSIfoPB"}
